import org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;
import static org.junit.jupiter.api.Assertions.*;

public class CalculatorTest {

    @Test
    void testAddition() {
        assertEquals(10, 5 + 5);
    }
}
________________________________________
Conclusion
JUnit is a powerful testing framework in Java that simplifies unit testing through annotations, assertions, and automation support. It plays a key role in ensuring software quality, making it essential in modern DevOps and Agile development environments.
